Hellplague:
 
Hellplague continued on her course, toward Maximal Base.  If her sister was safe there, there was a good chance she could find safety there.  And with Celeron, she could possibly get on the leader's good side.  She could only hope.
 
"Hellplague hailing Maximal fortification.  I wish to negotiate an amistice," she said, a comm channel connecting to Maximal Base.
